## Legal Disclaimer

This project contains legal documents sourced from the official United States
Government Publishing Office (GPO) through GovInfo.gov. These documents are
public domain materials of the United States federal government.

The original legal documents remain the property of the United States government
and are subject to their terms of use. This project provides tools and 
infrastructure for accessing, converting, and analyzing these public domain
legal documents.

Users should verify the accuracy and currency of legal information with official
sources before making any legal decisions based on this data.

## Data Attribution

Legal documents in this repository are sourced from:
- **Source**: U.S. Government Publishing Office (GPO)
- **Website**: https://www.govinfo.gov/app/collection/uscode
- **Format**: USLM (United States Legislative Markup) XML
- **License**: Public Domain (U.S. Federal Government)
- **Last Updated**: January 2024

## Official Sources

For official, authoritative versions of the United States Code, please refer to:
- **Office of the Law Revision Counsel**: https://uscode.house.gov/
- **GovInfo.gov**: https://www.govinfo.gov/app/collection/uscode
- **Legal Information Institute**: https://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode

## Third-Party Tools

This project uses various open-source tools and libraries:
- **curl**: Data download (MIT-style license)
- **jq**: JSON processing (MIT license)
- **xmllint**: XML parsing (MIT license)
- **pandoc**: Document processing (GPL v2+)
- **bash**: Scripting environment (GPL v3+)

Please refer to individual tool licenses for their specific terms.
